item.title: evalbox - pyjail writeup
item.description: This was a particularly unique and well-designed PyJail challenge featured in the Asian Cyber Security Challenge. Although I solved it during the contest using an unintended method, I later came across a writeup by ptr-yudai (an incredible pwner, someone I really aspire to be like!). Below are the notes I made while going through his insightful writeup.
